國立交通大學機構典藏：壓電陶瓷纖維複材平板導波特性的實驗及數值分析






























































Please click here if you are not redirected within a few seconds.
Skip navigation
















目前位置：國立交通大學機構典藏
學術出版
畢業論文






















標題: 壓電陶瓷纖維複材平板導波特性的實驗及數值分析Experimental and Numerical Characterization of Guided Wave Propagation in Piezoelectric Ceramic Fiber Composite Plates
作者: 黃招喜Huang, Jhao-Si尹慶中Yin, Ching-Chung機械工程系所
關鍵字: 壓電陶瓷纖維複材;準矢面板波;準水平偏極板波;雷射超音波;頻散曲線;piezoelectric fiber composite;quasi-sagittal plate wave;quasi- transverse horizontal plate wave;laser ultrasound;dispersion curves
公開日期: 2015
摘要: 壓電陶瓷纖維複材是由相同方向排列的壓電纖維、環氧樹脂及兩層聚醯亞胺所構成的三明治結構。原本抗拉性差的壓電纖維埋入環氧樹脂，後者分擔張應力，使壓電纖維複材具有可撓性，又不失其主動性能。本研究以實驗及數值分析未極化之壓電陶瓷纖維複材的板波波傳，瞭解纖維排列方向對於板波頻散特性的影響。採用Nd:YAG脈衝雷射為板波激發源，壓力波及剪力波探頭感測板波，以步進馬達驅動之光學平臺沿波傳方向線性掃描，將多筆單點時域訊號排列成時間與空間域的B掃描灰階圖，以二維快速傅立葉轉換獲得導波頻散曲線。數值模擬採用有限元素法套裝軟體，分析板波在壓電陶瓷纖維複材平板的頻散特性及自然模態。在不平行於纖維的波傳方向上，沒有純粹的矢面波及水平偏極波，準矢面板波與準水平偏極板波都具有特定的位移偏振角。數值模擬及實驗結果顯示，剪力波探頭具備同時量測任意波傳方向之板波頻散曲線的能力。Piezoelectric fiber composites are made of unidirectional piezoelectric ceramic fibers embedded in epoxy resin and sandwiched between two polyimide films. With assistance of the extensible epoxy resin, the originally brittle piezoelectric ceramic fibers become flexible and have no loss of active ability. This thesis experimentally and numerically studies plate wave propagation in a non-poled piezoelectric fiber composite to understand fiber orientation depending dispersive characteristics. A Nd:YAG pulsed laser was used to stimulate plate waves. The point sources separated by a constant interval were linearly scanned by a stepper driving optical stage in the wave propagating direction. The B-scan data captured by a pressure wave transducer or a shear wave transducer were arranged in time and space domain. Dispersion spectra were achieved by a two-dimensional fast Fourier transform. The dispersive characteristics and modal deformations of plate waves in the piezoelectric fiber composite were also determined by use of a commercial finite-element code. There are neither pure sagittal plate waves nor transverse horizontal (TH) plate waves in off-axis propagation. Specific polarization angle can be discovered in the quasi-sagittal plate wave and quasi-TH plate wave. Numerical and experimental evidence indicates that shear wave transducers are capable of measuring dispersion curves for plate wave propagation in arbitrary directions.
URI: http://140.113.39.130/cdrfb3/record/nctu/#GT070251075http://hdl.handle.net/11536/127447
顯示於類別：畢業論文




















IR@NCTUTAIRCrossRefFlexible Ultrasonic Transducers for Transverse Horizontal Plate Waves / Yin, Ching-Chung;Tsai, Wei-Che水平偏振超聲導波之壓電纖維複材換能器 / 蔡瑋哲;Tasi, Wei-Zhe;尹慶中;Yin, Ching-ChungFlexible Ultrasonic Transducers Using Piezoelectric Fiber Composites with Antisymmetric Interdigital Electrodes / Yin, Ching-Chung;Wu, Yu-Chien;Liu, Yu-Shyan;Hsu, Shih-Ming具指叉電極壓電纖維複材導波換能器 / 陳勁希;Chen, Jing-Si;尹慶中;Yin, Ching-Chung板波波傳為基礎之複材層板結構健康監測研究 / 劉育翔;Yu-shyan Liu;尹慶中;Ching-Chung Yin光纖光柵在板波波傳量測上的應用 / 李雨青;Yu-Ching Lee;尹慶中;Dr. Ching-Chung Yin具反對稱指插電極之壓電纖維複材超音波換能器及應用 / 尹慶中;YIN CHING-CHUNG元培科技大學 - 壓電陶瓷複合層板面內模態振動特性實驗與數值分析 / 林育志 國立臺灣大學 - 部分電極壓電陶瓷板的動態特性分析及實驗(2/2) / 馬劍清 元培科技大學 - PVDF壓電薄膜與壓電陶瓷元件振動特性實驗與數值分析及其在觸覺感測上的應用與功能評估 / 林育志 國立臺灣大學 - 壓電纖維複材與壓電陶瓷雙晶片的動態特性及應用於能量擷取系統之探討 / 曾國舜; Tseng, Kuo-Shun 國立臺灣大學 - 石英壓電板的振動特性分析及實驗 / 馬劍清 國立成功大學 - 金屬平板與玻璃纖維強化塑膠平板承受暫態氣體震波負載之實驗與數值分析研究 / 段明廷; Duan, Ming-Ting Loading...

















冶金與陶瓷實驗室 - 材料科學與工程系 




